name: Nintendo Switch Vector
description:
Nintendo Switch Vector

A fully vector illustration of the Nintendo Switch. You can toggle to the default Grey joycons from the Fill section of the Properties Panel. You can change the fill of the screen to a illustration or image of a game for mockups.
